text: Mitrella noel is a species of sea snail in the family Columbellidae, the dove snails. ==Distribution== The species is endemic to the island of São Tomé. ==References== *Rolán E. & Gori S. (2009). Two new species of the genera Jujubinus and Mitrella (Mollusca, Prosobranchia) from Sao Tomé Island. Gloria Maris 48(1): 10–16. noel Category:Endemic fauna of São Tomé Island Category:Gastropods described in 2009
title: Mitrella noel
